 with PURGE_CHUNK_SIZE=5000\n- WAL-bounded iteration\n- Daily interval scheduling\n\n**Resolution**: This idea has been **implemented**. The unified `RetentionPolicy` class (in `retentionPolicy.ts`) now:\n- Parameterizes retention by `{table, cutoffColumn, chunkSize, safetyFraction?, preDeleteAggregator?}`\n- Allows each table to register its lifecycle declaratively rather than re-implementing the loop\n- Ensures that bug fixes, safety improvements, and observability enhancements apply everywhere at once\n- Uses a centralized pattern that was solidified from this architectural insight\n\n**Effort**: 4 | **Impact**: 6 | **Risk**: 3"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a54fdcbb5119672a4 (use SendMessage with to: 'a54fdcbb5119672a4' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 43680\ntool_uses: 35\nduration_ms: 166082</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a406f229-b97a-4ebf-a68f-d55c6981f4d6","uuid":"14bfe39f-e907-441f-8fdc-220c9425db71","timestamp":"2026-03-18T18:14:07.734Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Search thoroughly for a file related to \"idea-821b5673-unify-retention-into-declarati\" in the project at C:\\Users\\kazda\\kiro\\personas-cloud. This could be a requirement file, idea file, or planning document. Search:\n1. All directories including hidden ones (.claude, .planning, .gsd, etc.)\n2. Any files containing \"821b5673\" in their name or content\n3. Any files containing \"unify-retention\" or \"retention-declarati\" in name or content\n4. Any \"ideas\" or \"requirements\" directories\n5. Check the user's home directory .claude folder too: C:\\Users\\kazda\\.claude\n\nBe very thorough - search by glob patterns and also grep file contents.","agentId":"a54fdcbb5119672a4","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information. Let me compile my findings.\n\n## Summary\n\nI've thoroughly searched for the file related to \"idea-821b5673-unify-retention-into-declarati\" and found comprehensive information. Here