s that bug fixes, safety improvements, and observability enhancements apply everywhere at once\n- Uses a centralized pattern that was solidified from this architectural insight\n\n**Effort**: 4 | **Impact**: 6 | **Risk**: 3"}],"totalDurationMs":166082,"totalTokens":43680,"totalToolUseCount":35,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5977,"cache_read_input_tokens":37054,"output_tokens":642,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5977},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
